  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installasjon av libkdcraw</title>

    <para>Installer <application>libkdcraw</application> ved å kjøre
    følgende kommandoer:</para>

<screen><userinput>sed -e '/3/a add_definitions(${KDE4_ENABLE_EXCEPTIONS})' \
        -i libkdcraw/CMakeLists.txt &amp;&amp;

mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir;   \
      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release           \
      -DCMAKE_MINIMUM_REQUIRED_VERSION=3.0 \
      -Wno-dev .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Nå, som <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> bruker:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

 <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Parameterforklaringer</title>

